snippet.title: Pokémon Graffiti Eraser (*NEW* Mini-Game~ Pokémon Global Link)
snippet.description:
Playing Graffiti Eraser in Global Link, here i am trying to get a Lucky Egg, with no luck hahaha!. Hope someday to reach for it =D.

Something really cool is that if you get Shaymin or Arceus, you gain 50 pts, that means a free Rank C, try to get a good rank to win a better item, but, i really think is a random price.
